esent in the early stage of the ELM. The results for\na n=2 RMP from the ELM control coils show the expected n=2 footprint structure.\nThe results for the mitigated ELM show a similar structure, modulated by a\nhigher n perturbation of the ELM, consistent with our theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2016 19:13:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-13"}
